[[File:Crimson-Stormtrooper.png|thumb|right|150px|A magma trooper.]]
'''Magma stormtroopers''', commonly referred to as '''magma troopers''' or '''lavatroopers''', were a specialized division of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Stormtrooper/Legends|stormtroopers]]. Specifically trained to operate in active geologic vents, they were responsible for crushing revolts and other insurgent actions on volcanic [[Mining/Legends|mining]] [[Planet/Legends|planets]] such as [[Mustafar/Legends|Mustafar]] and [[Sullust/Legends|Sullust]], as well as defending any volcanic mines filled with rare ores from Rebel guerrillas. [[Magma/Legends|Magma]] trooper armor was specially designed to withstand extremely high temperatures, including some direct contact with volcanic magma. The armor was reinforced with [[Duravlex]], and is capable of withstanding extreme temperatures of up to 1,900 degrees centigrade. Magma troopers were also equipped with [[SS-Mobile-tech flamethrower]]s and heavy blasters.

